---
import Tilt from "react-parallax-tilt";
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import profile from "@assets/images/profile.png";
---

<section>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row justify-evenly items-center p-10 md:pt-56 md:px-20 gap-10 md:gap-20 text-white"
  >
    <div
      class="w-full xl:w-3/4 2xl:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-10 backdrop-blur-sm bg-fgreen/5 p-5 rounded-lg"
    >
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-center xl:text-left px-5 w-full">
        A little <span class="text-fgreen">review</span> about me
      </h1>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start text-justify px-5 gap-2 md:gap-5 md:text-lg"
      >
        <p>
          <span id="year_ago"></span> years ago I discovered programming and it has
          been the best thing that has happened to me ... üòç
        </p>

        <p>
          I have experience in classical languages ‚Äã‚Äãsuch as: <span
            class="text-fgreen font-bold italic"
            >Java, Kotlin, Python & C++</span
          ><br />(Though the last two I'm pretty rusty üòÖ)
        </p>

        <p>
          My areas of interest are:&nbsp; <span
            class="text-fgreen font-medium italic"
            >Android, Backend & Blockchain</span
          >
        </p>

        <p>
          Lately I've been interacting with new tools and areas like:&nbsp;
          <span class="text-fgreen italic font-bold">UE5, Unity & AR/VR</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-20">
      <Tilt client:load>
        <Picture
          src={profile}
          formats={["webp", "png"]}
          class="rounded-full border-2 border-fgreen border-solid hover:shadow-fgreen duration-150 ease-in-out hover:scale-105"
          alt="Avatar"
          fallbackFormat="png"
        />
      </Tilt>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    let diffAnno = new Date().getFullYear() - 2013;

    const yearElement = document.getElementById("year_ago");
    if (yearElement) {
      yearElement.textContent = diffAnno.toString();
    } else {
      console.log('No se encontr√≥ el elemento con id "year"');
    }
  </script>
</section>
